Super Clean theme for Trello.
You can use this theme for Card-Sorting and simple task-management & etc.
You can use this Userstyles theme for Wikipedia with Stylish/Stylus extension in any browser.

Source code <a href="https://github.com/sirpooya/Stylish">available on Github.</a>
Please <a href="https://github.com/sirpooya/Stylish/issues">report issues here.</a> Or comment below.

Check out the <a href="https://userstyles.org/styles/164018">Glassy Theme</a>.
more info about me: <a href="http://pooya.ml">pooya.ml</a>

